---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Portugal Airport Car Rental Comparisons | TripAxle"
  description="Compare car rental pickup options at Portugal’s main airports."
>
  <section class="hero">
    <p class="eyebrow">Airport comparisons</p>
    <h1>Compare Portugal’s main airport pickup options.</h1>
    <p class="intro">
      Use these guides to compare car rental pickup options at Lisbon, Porto,
      and Faro before you reserve.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="airport-grid">
    <article class="airport-card">
      <h2>Lisbon Airport</h2>
      <p>
        Best for travelers leaving the city quickly, but not always ideal for
        city-only stays.
      </p>
      <a href="#">Lisbon Airport guide →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="airport-card">
      <h2>Porto Airport</h2>
      <p>
        A strong starting point for northern Portugal road trips and flexible
        multi-stop itineraries.
      </p>
      <a href="#">Porto Airport guide →</a>
    </article>

    <article class="airport-card">
      <h2>Faro Airport</h2>
      <p>
        Often the key pickup point for Algarve trips, beach stays, and southern
        Portugal driving routes.
      </p>
      <a href="/faro-airport-car-rental">Faro Airport guide →</a>
    </article>
  </section>

  <section class="content-grid">
    <article class="main-card">
      <h2>What these airport guides will cover</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Whether the airport is a smart place to rent for your trip</li>
        <li>Common pickup and return issues to watch for</li>
        <li>Which booking platforms fit each airport best</li>
        <li>Who should rent there and who may not need to</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>How to use this hub</h2>
      <p>
        Start with the airport that matches your arrival city. Then use the
        guide to decide whether airport pickup is the best choice, or whether
        town pickup or no rental at all makes more sense.
      </p>
    </article>

    <aside class="side-card">
      <h2>Planned airport pages</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Lisbon Airport car rental comparison</li>
        <li>Porto Airport car rental comparison</li>
        <li>Faro Airport car rental comparison</li>
      </ul>
    </aside>
  </section>

  <style>
    .hero {
      padding: 2rem 0 2.25rem;
      max-width: 760px;
    }

    .eyebrow {
      margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
      color: #2f6fed;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      font-weight: 700;
      text-transform: uppercase;
      letter-spacing: 0.04em;
    }

    h1 {
      margin: 0;
      font-size: clamp(2.1rem, 5vw, 3.6rem);
      line-height: 1.08;
    }

    .intro {
      margin-top: 1rem;
      color: #5b5b55;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      max-width: 680px;
    }

    .airport-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
      gap: 1rem;
      margin-bottom: 1rem;
    }

    .airport-card,
    .main-card,
    .side-card {
      background: white;
      border: 1px solid #e4e4de;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.25rem;
    }

    .airport-card h2,
    .main-card h2,
    .side-card h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
    }

    .airport-card p {
      color: #5b5b55;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }

    .airport-card a {
      font-weight: 600;
      color: #2f6fed;
    }

    .content-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: 2fr 1fr;
      gap: 1rem;
    }

    ul {
      padding-left: 1.2rem;
    }

    li + li {
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 900px) {
      .airport-grid,
      .content-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }
  </style>
</Layout>